quran[9{c,v,t}:
3,53,"maalik! jo farmaan to ne nazil kya hai hum ne usay maan liya aur rasool ki pairwi qubool ki, hamara naam gawahi dainay walon mein likh le """
3,54,phir bani Israel ( maseeh ke khilaaf ) khufia tadbeerye karne lagey jawab mein Allah ne bhi apni khufia tadbeer ki aur aisi tdbiron mein Allah sab se barh kar hai
3,55,"( woh Allah ki khufia tadbeer hi thi ) jab uss ne kaha ke,"" ae eesa! ab mein tujhe wapas le lon ga aur tujh ko apni taraf utha lon ga aur jinhon ne tera inkaar kya hai unn se ( yani un ki mayt se aur un ke ganday mahol mein un ke sath rehne se ) tujhe pak kar dun ga aur teri pairwi karne walon ko qayamat taq un logon par baladst rakhon ga jinhon ne tera inkaar kya hai phir tum sab ko aakhir mere paas aana hai, uss waqt mein unn baton ka faisla kar dun ga jin mein tumahray darmain ikhtilaaf howa hai"
3,56,jin logon ne kufar o inkaar ki rawish ikhtiyar ki hai inhen duniya aur akhirat dono mein sakht saza dun ga aur woh koi madadgaar nah payen ge
3,57,"aur jinhon ne imaan aur naik amli ka rawayya ikhtiyar kya hai inhen unn ke ajar poooray poooray day diye jayen ge aur khoob jaan le ke zaalmon se Allah hargiz mohabbat nahi karta """
3,58,yeh ayaat aur hikmat se labraiz tazkeray hain jo hum tumhe suna rahay hain
3,59,Allah ke nazdeek eesa ki misaal Aadam ki si hai ke Allah ne usay matti se peda kya aur hukum diya ke ho ja aur woh ho gaya
3,60,yeh asal haqeeqat hai jo tumahray Rab ki taraf se batayi ja rahi hai aur tum un logon mein shaamil nah ho jo is mein shak karte hain
3,61,"yeh ilm aa jaane ke baad ab koi is maamla mein tum se jhagra kere to ae MuhammadSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ! is se kaho,"" aao hum aur tum khud bhi aa jayen aur apne apne baal bachon ko bhi le ayen aur Kkhuda se dua karen ke jo jhoota ho uss par khuda ki laanat ho """
